","year":-445},{"id":"reclZu7c9j7Z3dJkb","ref":"Neh.11.4","text":"And at Jerusalem dwelt certain of the children of Judah, and of the children of Benjamin. Of the children of Judah; Athaiah the son of Uzziah, the son of Zechariah, the son of Amariah, the son of Shephatiah, the son of Mahalaleel, of the children of Perez;","year":-445},{"id":"recUFK5W9RbupiMnN","ref":"Neh.11.5","text":"And Maaseiah the son of Baruch, the son of Colhozeh, the son of Hazaiah, the son of Adaiah, the son of Joiarib, the son of Zechariah, the son of Shiloni.","year":-445},{"id":"rectX4OPTYVdgyyaR","ref":"Neh.11.6","text":"All the sons of Perez that dwelt at Jerusalem were four hundred threescore and eight valiant men.","year":-445},{"id":"recqPK4TcORJ6TR9q","ref":"Neh.11.7","text":"And these are the sons of Benjamin; Sallu the son of Meshullam, the son of Joed, the son of Pedaiah, the son of Kolaiah, the son of Maaseiah, the son of Ithiel, the son of Jesaiah.","year":-445},{"id":"recImkHuv1vFrh5BH","ref":"Neh.11.8","text":"And after him Gabbai, Sallai, nine hundred twenty and eight.","year":-445}]}
